Package: freestiler
Title: Create Vector Tiles from Spatial Data
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2026-06-24
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kyle", "Walker", , "kyle@walker-data.com", role = c("aut", "rev")),
    person("Jimmy", "Briggs", , "jimmy.briggs@noclocks.dev", role = "ctb",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7489-8787"))
  )
Description: A forked, windows-specific build of the original freestiler
    package which provides features to create vector tile archives in
    'PMTiles' format from 'sf' spatial data frames. Supports 'Mapbox
    Vector Tile' ('MVT') and 'MapLibre Tile' ('MLT') output formats. Uses
    a 'Rust' backend via 'extendr' for fast, in-memory tiling with zero
    external system dependencies.
